WEBVTT

00:03:57.151 --> 00:04:00.240
there is a concentration

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:04.491
of knowledge, of understanding, of clout.

00:04:04.491 --> 00:04:06.578
I mean, think about it:

00:04:06.578 --> 00:04:09.993
How does a friendship become a subsidy?

00:04:09.993 --> 00:04:11.270
Seamlessly,

00:04:11.270 --> 00:04:13.905
when a senior government official decides

00:04:13.905 --> 00:04:16.402
to leave government and become a lobbyist

00:04:16.402 --> 00:04:18.316
for a private interest

00:04:18.316 --> 00:04:21.018
and convert his or her relationships into capital

00:04:21.018 --> 00:04:23.325
for their new masters.

